  "body": "https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-solidity/blob/4c6575bf2fdf97af517b9c1aea886125bab8c4af/contracts/crowdsale/validation/WhitelistedCrowdsale.sol#L11\r\n\r\nWhen we inherit a contract with Whitelisted and other types of crowdsales, it causes the above said issue.\r\n\r\nThe fix was to swap the order of Whitelist and Crowdsale. Hence changing \r\n\r\ncontract WhitelistedCrowdsale is Whitelist, Crowdsale {\r\n\r\nto \r\n\r\ncontract WhitelistedCrowdsale is Crowdsale, Whitelist {\r\n\r\nFixes the issue",
