    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is because Solidity supports multiple inheritance through [C3 linearization](https://solidity.readthedocs.io/en/v0.4.24/contracts.html#multiple-inheritance-and-linearization), disallowing some inheritance graphs. While annoying, there's not much we can do about it, and as far as I know, there aren't any cases in OZ where this prevents compilation.",
